{
  "stem": "11593.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "They didn't know what's going to happen next.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "They were not in the city for more than two months, where they hunted down 400 people, who I would say, most of them, 380 Jews and 20 Christians.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "They took them in a valley behind the cement factory and shot them in cold blood and machine-gunned them.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I was able to escape through a window and ran away from that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And when they chased me, one of my Polish friends showed the Ukrainian militiamen the wrong direction.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Instead of telling them I went right, they told them I went to the left side.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I went into the wheat fields.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And at night, I came back to the house.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Everything-- the-- the-- the action, what do you call it, was over.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "That happened in August, I believe, of 1941.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nothing happened to the house.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were hunting people, just going into homes on the streets and picking up people, mostly Jews, you know?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And put them in on the trucks.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They chased.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It-- I saw that, so I ran away.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were not-- they not opportunity to pick me up.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- I jumped through the back window, running to the--",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--wheat fields, you know?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And as I found out, when they said, where is he, one of the Polish boys told them, he went to the other direction.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father escaped also, and my grandfather escape.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But they shot my father's oldest brother in that particular action.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Around the end of August, or the beginning of September, our city saw a German engineer.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That had set up an office and explained to the people that they're going to have two German companies.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "One was called Joseph Aung, A-U-N-G, and the other one Todt Organisation.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They going to employ a lot of people.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
